br />\n<br />\n重有依2個月好多單左膠死攬傷人者<br />\n根本班撚樣只係為光環 欺善怕惡<br />\n對住黑社會就淆底唔敢阻黑社會斬人<br />\n對住自己手足 知手足唔會打佢地<br />\n就大大力阻手足還拖 同講廢話訓前線話<br />\n話會扣幾多分 會失民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"aa9c2ff32aa03720f5bebd699c78830f05218cf1","tid":1550541,"uid":60785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:45:20.000Z","msg":"下次應該打柒左膠"},{"pid":"ebe54b284e7ed5a4216d684606d7f6791dbf0bf8","tid":1550541,"uid":296677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eb82d7b29dd51bcbab4fa9e8d9318caa1a7f4637","tid":1550541,"uid":82359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ab1a4a3971e47ba945e3a8c6ebb7ae9e10f39ec7","tid":1550541,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:30:37.000Z","msg":"次撚次都係你地累事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:36:40.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過個啲可能唔係左膠係臥底，所以下次打埋佢地啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:48:15.000Z","msg":"有無發現<br />\n藍屍砍人打人佢唔出黎架<br />\n黃人一打就會上水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b52bddc638bfac99aa104ef9ed2a34decf68477","tid":1550541,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"707ee1a7be944a62bd07d30a2e4259c9900fbd3b","tid":1550541,"uid":121937,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8778d0a873e4e78ce5fffa1bdd4d178860c87eae","tid":1550541,"uid":81154,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:33:37.000Z","msg":"其實有冇諗過左膠係中共請番來，就好似網上d網軍咁，用另一種方式解散行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:35:04.000Z","msg":"不如話係黑警喬裝仲有說服力<br />\n次撚次都係佢地幫手拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:54:21.000Z","msg":"應該都9成係<br />\n黑面白面一野做哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a931466b77259bf